{"type": "article", "id": 4491, "title": "Spring 极简衣柜", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-18T07:41:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233606LcqYtealFZG0hdz6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t德国品牌 fifti-fifti 日前邀请德国设计师 Maximilian Schmahl 设计了一款极简衣柜 Spring。你可能会提出质疑，这不就是两个三角形的白色支架搭配一根横杆嘛，也能叫衣柜？但在设计师 Maximilian Schmahl 看来，正是因为其简单的结构和造型，才使得 Spring 几乎能够适应于安装在任何场所。榉木材质的挂衣杆被两头姥姥固定在墙上的三角白色钢丝架支起来，就可以轻松挂置任何衣物了。此外，Spring 还能根据需要调节长度，对于租房一族来说，实在是节省空间而又方便拆卸的利器。定价 119 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.fifti-fifti.net/en/catalog/spring.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233604g8CflLy2SUXNaJtp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233605OYMox8UlT0VSeLaj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.471875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233605lkgbfuzhB8DiQmWC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}